nt||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Now, let us talk about the defense. dee is certainly right to want to lead clubs. However, as I have mentioned in the past, leading an unprotected ace against a suit is rarely right, and often wrong.  And in this case it did give up a trick.  My choice would have probably been a heart, as I am long in both of the opps side suits. The other issue on defense is lisa's ruffing of spades at trick nine. lisa should ruff the K of spades at trick eight.|
